BenchmarkCurve.description: Specifies a benchmark curve name. Possible ISO 20022 compliant values are: WIBOR, Treasury, TIBOR, TELBOR, SWAP, STIBOR, PRIBOR, Pfandbriefe, NIBOR, MuniAAA, MOSPRIM, LIBOR, LIBID, JIBAR, ISDAFIX, GCFRepo, FutureSWAP, EuroSwiss, EURODOLLAR, Euribor, EONIASwaps, EONIA, CIBOR, CDOR, BUBOR, BBSW
